    "is_free": false,
    "description": "在经历了多年城市的喧嚣生活后，你决定做出一个大胆的选择——搬到乡村。意外的是，你继承了一座传承了几代的老农场。被这种变化的可能性吸引，你决定告别城市生活，踏上前往乡村的旅程。<br><br>抵达后，你发现这个农场需要大量修复才能恢复昔日的辉煌。在翻找老房子时，你发现了一本古老的园艺书——一本家族日记，里面记录了几代人种植稀有蔬菜的宝贵经验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挖掘</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/cf86157b0f1741e0aaf81c765a0036d9.poster.avif?t=1765312190\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/cf86157b0f1741e0aaf81c765a0036d9.webm?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/cf86157b0f1741e0aaf81c765a0036d9.mp4?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>挖掘和松动土壤，为植物创造最佳的生长条件。同时，要注意土壤的质量、湿度和养分含量，这些因素都会影响蔬菜的健康成长。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生长</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/d025de78fba4b849bc1d5042da8af24e.poster.avif?t=1765312190\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/d025de78fba4b849bc1d5042da8af24e.webm?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/d025de78fba4b849bc1d5042da8af24e.mp4?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>无论是传统品种还是稀有独特的品种，你都可以尝试自己种植。你可以选择直接在土壤中种植，也可以在花盆里种植。除了购买现成的幼苗，你还可以用稀有且可靠的种子自行繁育。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >学习</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/6455f4a309460bbeb382181ad7cf135f.poster.avif?t=1765312190\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/6455f4a309460bbeb382181ad7cf135f.webm?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/6455f4a309460bbeb382181ad7cf135f.mp4?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>学会了解蔬菜的需求，根据它们的具体情况调整施肥、浇水和保护措施。应对害虫和植物病害的挑战，使用天然的保护方法和有机产品来保护你的作物。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关爱</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/18687eca9bce126e7a3e931299225659.poster.avif?t=1765312190\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/18687eca9bce126e7a3e931299225659.webm?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/18687eca9bce126e7a3e931299225659.mp4?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每种植物都需要独特的照料。修剪、引导嫩枝、用绳子绑扎，并建立支撑，以确保植物的最佳生长和更高的产量。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >销售</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/060ed108f7fbda462c281be79e06f35d.poster.avif?t=1765312190\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/060ed108f7fbda462c281be79e06f35d.webm?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/060ed108f7fbda462c281be79e06f35d.mp4?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>收获你的作物，将它们销售给注重品质和新鲜度的本地商店和超市。接收订单，与买家建立良好的关系，并协商价格。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进步</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/d040ef6b1047b9cf57145f9bfc60ca08.poster.avif?t=1765312190\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/d040ef6b1047b9cf57145f9bfc60ca08.webm?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185200/extras/d040ef6b1047b9cf57145f9bfc60ca08.mp4?t=1765312190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>把赚到的钱投入到农场的发展中。购买新工具，扩展田地，建设更多温室和灌溉系统。每项投资都有它的作用，可以帮助你根据植物的需求优化生长条件，让你的农场蓬勃发展！",
